{"_id":"Speed Dial Folder","title":"Speed Dial for Android","icon":"icon-mobile-phone","dateCreated":"2010-10-22T22:00:00.000Z","isProd":true,"desc":"After 3x3Links took of, the demand for a companion Android app grew. Back than there were no folders on the Android 1.x homescreen, so this app was a perfect folder replacement.

